## âœ¨ Features

- **User Authentication** â€“ Sign up, log in with email/password or social providers (Google, GitHub)
- **Property Listings** â€“ Create, view, and manage property listings with detailed information
- **Reservations** â€“ Book properties for specific dates, manage your trips
- **Property Management** â€“ Manage your properties and view reservations made by guests
- **Search & Filtering** â€“ Find properties by location, dates, guests, and property features
- **Categories** â€“ Browse properties by categories like Beach, Modern, Countryside, etc.
- **Favorites** â€“ Save properties to your favorites list
- **Responsive Design** â€“ Fully responsive UI that works on all devices

